node.text:
A longtime favorite of local skiers and riders, Traverse City's @mtholiday is a true community ski area.
 
While winter fun is always on the agenda during the snowy season, Mt. Holiday is also a gathering place for locals and visitors alike, with a friendly atmosphere to make you feel right at home. Ride along as our guide Otie explores Upper Holiday and Northwind, and feel the thrills and chills of snow tubing under the lights.
 
We'll explore a new ski area each week as we #SkiPureMichigan all winter long. Visit the link in our bio to discover more signature runs at ski areas across #PureMIchigan.

node.title: Ski Pure Michigan | Mt Holiday Ski Area

node.text:
We cherish the moments made by memories next to a campfire in the Michigan woods, at our favorite restaurants and breweries—those memories made by yearly summer trips to the cabin, to Mackinac Island, or to the general “Up North.” Even though travelling isn’t business as usual, rest assured #PureMichigan will always be here to welcome you back to the places where memories are made. For National Travel & Tourism Week, that’s the #SpiritOfTravel. 
To plan a trip for the future or explore what our state has to offer, start at michigan.org. You can also explore our curated list of virtual travel experiences at michigan.org/virtualtravel. #NTTW2020
